OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Frain moves eastwards overnight, heavy
OL,7,Fat times, clearing the east by
OL,8,Fmorning. Clearer spells and showers
OL,9,Ffollow. Increasingly windy,
OL,10,Fparticularly in the northwest with
OL,11,Fgales, locally severe, developing.
OL,12,FChilly but staying frost free.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FBright with sunny spells
OL,15,Fand showers, these most frequent in
OL,16,Fthe northwest, where they could be
OL,17,Fheavy with thunder. Temperatures near
OL,18,Faverage but feeling cooler in the
OL,19,Fongoing blustery winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
